{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/Artboard_1.png?t=1737474820\" /><br>Set in a 90's retro future, Inertial Drift is an Arcade Racer with a devastatingly unique handling model and unbelievably satisfying twin-stick drift mechanics. Inertial Drift offers a whole new level of accessibility and challenge to the arcade racing genre - for a driving experience genuinely unlike anything you've played before.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/Artboard_2.png?t=1737474820\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/unique_twin_stick_controls.gif?t=1737474820\" /><br>The left stick is used for steering, while the right hand <strong>Drift Stick</strong> gives you independent control over your drift. Intuitive for new players and uniquely challenging for pros. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/Artboard_3.png?t=1737474820\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/Fiercely_Individual_Cars.gif?t=1737474820\" /><br>Each one of the <strong>16 cars</strong> is a totally different beast, with unique characteristics to master. Get behind the wheel of Sport hatchbacks, Coupe's, Supercars &amp; more! <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/Artboard_4.png?t=1737474820\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/20_tracks.gif?t=1737474820\" /><br>Tear through neon city streets, race around rural temple complexes and hurtle down winding mountain passes. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/Artboard_5.png?t=1737474820\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/Set_in_a_90s_retro_future.gif?t=1737474820\" /><br>Each racetrack is set within a bold and distinctive environment. Including vibrant cityscapes, coastal sunsets, gorgeous starry skies and snow-capped peaks. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/Artboard_6.png?t=1737474820\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/Single_Player_Story_Mode.gif?t=1737474820\" /><br>With <strong>7 race event types</strong> there is plenty of opportunity to perfect your craft! Get competitive in a mix of races, head-to-heads, time trials and style showdowns! <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/Artboard_7.png?t=1737474820\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1184480/extras/Multiplayer.gif?t=1737474820\" /><br>Think you've mastered the perfect drift? What better way to prove it. Take on other racers via <strong>local co-op and online multiplayer. </strong>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Oh... I Get It!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1184480/780b2f2ca7cf47c6d8c4c493dc40bdccca08aebb.jpg"},{"name":"Look Who's Finally Ready To Play","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1184480/7d7a4878a2fbfef3a1d34229b74c0446615b4e34.jpg"},{"name":"Start Your Engines!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1184480/3f375920fc6938a6852cacdae40c0d950abeef84.jpg"},{"name":"Take Care Of This Loser","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1184480/a0edc7dbcdc70de542e40adbe8c1f0ae65662016.jpg"},{"na